## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="dbeee-107">结合使用此方法<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A>方法<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dbeee-107">This method is used in conjunction with the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A> method of the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dbeee-108">特定重载<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A>方法调用查明重载应停止还是继续执行此类型的应用程序定义的回调方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dbeee-108">Certain overloads of the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A> method call an application-defined callback method of this type to find out if the overloads should stop or continue execution.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="dbeee-109">在执行期间，相关<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A>重载频繁调用此回调方法，以找出应停止绘制指定的映像是否应继续绘制图像。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dbeee-109">During execution, the relevant <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A> overloads frequently call this callback method to find out if they should stop drawing the specified image or if they should continue drawing the image.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dbeee-110"><xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImageAbort>回调方法可以确定是否要继续，或不基于包含在其中选择算法，由 callbackdata 参数 （可选） 使用的数据传递给它。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dbeee-110">The <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImageAbort> callback method can determine whether to continue or not based on a chosen algorithm included in it, optionally using the data passed to it by the callbackdata parameter.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dbeee-111">例如，算法可能会确定如果映像已滚动出屏幕和发出到取消信号<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A>方法来停止绘图。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dbeee-111">For example, an algorithm might determine if the image has scrolled off the screen and signal a cancellation to the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A> method to stop drawing.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="dbeee-112">此事件处理方法的用户声明必须具有与相同的参数<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImageAbort>委托声明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dbeee-112">A user declaration of this event-handling method must have the same parameters as the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImageAbort> delegate declaration.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="dbeee-113">此示例是一种简单的实现<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImageAbort>委托。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dbeee-113">This example is a simplistic implementation of the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImageAbort> delegate.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dbeee-114">它只检查是否<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A>方法已通过其使用 callbackdata 参数的数据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dbeee-114">It merely checks to see if the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A> method has passed it data using the callbackdata parameter.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dbeee-115">(某些<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A>重载仅具有`DrawImageAbort`参数并不传递任何数据; 某些重载同时具有`DrawImageAbort`和`callbackdata`参数并可以将数据传递。)如果已传递任何数据，它将返回`true`可以向调用发出信号<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A>它应当取消绘图的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dbeee-115">(Some <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A> overloads have only a `DrawImageAbort` parameter and pass no data; some overloads have both `DrawImageAbort` and `callbackdata` parameters and can pass data.) If no data was passed, it returns `true` to signal to the calling <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A> method that it should cancel the drawing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dbeee-116">如果已传递的数据，它将返回`false`以指示应继续绘图。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dbeee-116">If data was passed, it returns `false` to signal that drawing should continue.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="dbeee-117">此回调的实际实现会涉及一些条件，以取消或继续执行的实际的审查。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dbeee-117">A realistic implementation of this callback would involve the actual scrutiny of some criteria to cancel or continue the execution.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Private Function DrawImageCallback(callBackData As IntPtr) As Boolean  
     ' Test for call that passes callBackData parameter.  
     If callBackData.Equals(IntPtr.Zero) Then  
         ' If no callBackData passed, abort DrawImage method.  
         Return True  
     Else  
         ' If callBackData passed, continue DrawImage method.  
         Return False  
     End If  
 End Function 'DrawImageCallback  
```  
  
```csharp  
// Define DrawImageAbort callback method.  
 private bool DrawImageCallback(IntPtr callbackdata)  
 {  
    // Test for call that passes callBackData parameter.  
    if(callbackdata==IntPtr.Zero)  
    {  
       // If no callbackdata passed, cancel DrawImage method.  
       return true;  
    }  
    else  
    {  
       // If callbackdata passed, continue DrawImage method.  
       return false;  
    }  
 }  
```
